gather_pte_stats() connected to pmd_entry() does both of pmd loop and
pte loop. So this patch moves pte part into pte_entry().

ChangeLog v2:
- rebase onto mmots

Signed-off-by: Naoya Horiguchi <n-horiguchi@ah.jp.nec.com>
